content:
Use a Desk Phone

Answer and make voice calls from the Omni-Channel utility with a desk phone. 
Required user permissions: Contact Center Agent permission set.
The feature is available with Service Cloud Voice, using Amazon Connect or partner telephony.

Your admin must first set up desk phone functionality for your user profile in Amazon Connect.
Add the Phone component to the Voice Call page layout.
Voice is supported on Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, and Microsoft Edge (Chromium), with cookies enabled for single sign-on (SSO).

In the Omni-Channel utility, open the Phone tab. Select Desk Phone as the phone type, enter the desk phone number, and save your changes.

Now you can make and receive voice calls with your desk phone.
title: Setting Up a Desk Phone for Voice Calls in Service Cloud
